            <div class="event__info-text">
                                •••• GER bellow ••••<br />
<br />
ENG<br />
We are happy to invite you all at the Premiere of<br />
𝗘𝘅𝗲𝗿𝗰𝗶𝘀𝗲 𝗶𝗻 (𝗱𝗲)𝗰𝗼𝗻𝘀𝘁𝗿𝘂𝗰𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 - 𝗖𝗢𝗟𝗗 𝗟𝗜𝗣𝗦<br />
An installative dance performance in the large hall of 𝗭-𝗕𝗮𝘂.<br />
˜ Constant moving images. A fragile celebration of ambivalence and ambiguity. An exploration of dysfunctionality, a self-generated collapse that keeps creating new forms. An exercise towards transformation. ˜<br />
Concept, Choreography & performance : 𝔼𝕝𝕚𝕤𝕖 𝕃𝕦𝕕𝕚𝕟𝕒𝕣𝕕<br />
