<div class="layout-collapsible-section" id="cs3036569108">
    <h3 class="layout-collapsible-section__headline">
        <span class="layout-collapsible-section__headline-inner">Scheppercore</span>
        <span class="layout-collapsible-section__headline-more layout-collapsible-section__headline-more--collapsed">mehr</span>
        <span class="layout-collapsible-section__headline-less layout-collapsible-section__headline-less--collapsed">schliessen</span>
    </h3>
    <div class="layout-collapsible-section__body layout-collapsible-section__body--collapsed">
        <div class="layout">
<div class="layout-text">
    <p><span style="color: #212121;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: small;">Schepper was?<br />
Scheppercore ist eine Metal-Konzertreihe in Franken, Bayern und darüber hinaus. Wer Lust hat mitzuwirken, kann sich jederzeit über das Kontaktformular auf der <a href="https://www.scheppercore.de/">Scheppercore-Website</a> melden.<br />
Mehr Infos auf <a href="https://www.facebook.com/scheppercoreofficial/">Facebook</a> und <a href="https://www.instagram.com/scheppercore/">Instagram</a>.<br />
</span></span></span></p>
</div>
<div
    class="layout-image"
    style="padding-bottom: 66.650390625%;"
>
    
<img
    class="b-lazy"
    data-src="https://z-bau.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/2022Scheppercore-Team.jpeg"     data-src-small="https://z-bau.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/2022Scheppercore-Team-300x200.jpeg"     data-src-medium="https://z-bau.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/2022Scheppercore-Team-768x512.jpeg"     data-src-large="https://z-bau.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/2022Scheppercore-Team-1024x683.jpeg"     data-src-huge="https://z-bau.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/2022Scheppercore-Team-1400x933.jpeg"     data-src-giant="https://z-bau.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/2022Scheppercore-Team-2000x1333.jpeg"     data-src-enormous="https://z-bau.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/2022Scheppercore-Team.jpeg"     src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw=="
